{
  "stem": "268.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Buses are not running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How far can you walk in a day's time, until sundown?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we walked like that for three days, until the German Army caught up with us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was useless, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually they caught up the first day, but it just happened they didn't march into that town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were all around us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They encircled us, anyhow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's when the first few days of living under the German occupation began, which, as you know, lasted for almost a good five and a half years.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had one room, close to a main street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father said, we got to adjust, somehow, to this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This will not last long, maybe next-- a few weeks, a few months.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't have any furniture.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he says, I have to go back to Siemianowice and get the furniture.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is my furniture.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He came to the apartment-- and I didn't go with him, he went by himself, it was sealed already.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he went to see the authorities, said, I want my furniture.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm moving.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And first they gave him some run around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But somebody he knew there from the coal miners, too, who was then in the party, and they opened for him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he took a horse and buggy, rented from somebody, and took some furniture-- at least a bedroom, and tables and chairs, the essentials-- and moved into Czeladz.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we had some kind of a semblance of normalcy to start a new household.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the next thing he said, I got to go back to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But how do we-- the coal mines are taken over by the Germans now.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they established between Czeladz and Siemianowice, which was-- Czeladz was in Poland proper.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
